{
  "texts": [
    "This dataset offers Chinese dialogue resources, with each instruction accompanied by a label indicating the associated domain.",
    "• InstructionWild v1 (Ni et al, 2023).",
    "The InstructionWild v1 dataset furnishes 52K instructions in both Chinese and English.",
    "Constructed using a modelgenerated approach, the dataset involves providing five example prompts to the model, which then generates new instructions along with corresponding responses.",
    "The dataset is intended for non-commercial research purposes."
  ]
}